#: src/Form/AccessReindexFieldset.php:35
msgid ""
"<details>\n"
"    <summary>\n"
"        Propagation modes summary\n"
"    </summary>\n"
"    <p><em>The two options that control the propagation of status and "
"embargo dates are configured in the Settings tab. \"Propagation mode\" "
"applies only to this reindex job; a resource saved with the \"Apply "
"recursive\" option always uses \"overwrite\". \"Propagate embargo dates\" "
"applies anytime.</em></p>\n"
"    <p><strong>Access level</strong></p>\n"
"    <table class=\"access-propagation-table\">\n"
"        <thead>\n"
"            <tr>\n"
"                <th>Mode</th>\n"
"                <th>Child stricter than parent</th>\n"
"                <th>Child more permissive</th>\n"
"                <th>Child without status</th>\n"
"            </tr>\n"
"        </thead>\n"
"        <tbody>\n"
"            <tr>\n"
"                <th><code>skip if set</code> (default)</th>\n"
"                <td>Unchanged</td>\n"
"                <td>Unchanged (preserves \"free preview\" alongside a "
"\"forbidden\" original)</td>\n"
"                <td>New row created with the parent level</td>\n"
"            </tr>\n"
"            <tr>\n"
"                <th><code>max restrictive</code></th>\n"
"                <td>Kept (never demoted)</td>\n"
"                <td>Promoted to the parent level (breaks a deliberately free "
"child)</td>\n"
"                <td>New row created with the parent level</td>\n"
"            </tr>\n"
"            <tr>\n"
"                <th><code>overwrite</code></th>\n"
"                <td>Demoted to the parent level</td>\n"
"                <td>Promoted to the parent level</td>\n"
"                <td>New row created with the parent level</td>\n"
"            </tr>\n"
"        </tbody>\n"
"    </table>\n"
"    <p>In property mode, the level property value is also realigned from "
"access status after the parent value is written, so a child preserved at a "
"stricter level is never silently demoted at the next save.</p>\n"
"    <p><strong>Embargo dates</strong></p>\n"
"    <table class=\"access-propagation-table\">\n"
"        <thead>\n"
"            <tr>\n"
"                <th>Propagation embargo</th>\n"
"                <th>metadata mode</th>\n"
"                <th>property mode</th>\n"
"            </tr>\n"
"        </thead>\n"
"        <tbody>\n"
"            <tr>\n"
"                <th>Off</th>\n"
"                <td>Embargo columns untouched on every child. New rows get "
"null.</td>\n"
"                <td>Embargo property values left intact on every child.</"
"td>\n"
"            </tr>\n"
"            <tr>\n"
"                <th>On</th>\n"
"                <td>Parent embargo start/end copied per the chosen level "
"mode (skip if set, overwrite, max restrictive).</td>\n"
"                <td>Embargo property values rewritten from the post-"
"propagation access status.</td>\n"
"            </tr>\n"
"        </tbody>\n"
"    </table>\n"
"</details>"
msgstr ""

